Example:
```typescript
const researcher: SubAgent = {
  name: "researcher",
  description: "Research assistant",
  systemPrompt: "You are a researcher...",
  middleware: [myCustomMiddleware],  // Appended AFTER defaults
};

const agent = createDeepAgent({
  subagents: [researcher],
  // ...
});
```

The middleware is **appended after defaults**, so it runs outside/after the SDK's built-in middleware chain.

